  "Sec. I.-General Commandments. Concerning Covetousness. That We Ought Not to Return Injuries, Nor Revenge Ourselves on Him that Does Us Wrong.")
 (#P"/var/www/got/public/charito-wt/compiled-resources/anf07:26:12:12"
  "Sec. II.-Commandments to Men.  Concerning the Adornment of Ourselves, and the Sin Which Arises from Thence. That We Ought Not to Be Over-Curious About Those Who Live Wickedly, But to Be Intent Upon Our Own Proper Employment. What Books of Scripture We Ought to Read. That We Ought to Abstain from All the Books of Those that are Out of the Church. Concerning a Bad Woman.")
 (#P"/var/www/got/public/charito-wt/compiled-resources/anf07:26:12:14"
